  "title": "Administration & Human Resource Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Scope of Work</strong><br /></p><p><strong>General</strong></p><ul><li>Handle all requests, enquiries through phone or email quickly and professionally</li><li>Liaise with the various team members to handle such enquiries</li><li>Monitor office supply levels and order when appropriate</li><li>Develop and carry out an efficient documentation and filing system for both paper and electronic records</li><li>Delegate tasks as appropriate to other team members</li><li>Prepare reports by collecting, analysing, and summarising information</li></ul><p><strong>Human Resource</strong></p><ul><li>Liaise with various sources such as agencies for sourcing of manpower</li><li>Liaise with advertising agencies, as well as put up adverts on various sources for recruitment efforts</li><li>Prepare and maintain employment contracts using given templates</li><li>Maintain all documentation for personnel in a filing system</li><li>Use the company HR system for submission of payroll</li></ul>",
